{"tid":2409231,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［傷患］有無跑步/行山巴打有「鼠蹊部」痛問題？","createTime":"2021-02-15T15:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T23:56:06.000Z","uid":31361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfc1f0ac435f04bbeb44830b3cda8ee4728af33","tid":2409231,"uid":31361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上2星期行山行到左邊腳「鼠蹊部」，似拉傷，<br />\n頭幾日提腳都無力，3-4日後提到腳，但行路行10分鐘左右就開始痛⋯⋯⋯（左提腳，右提腳，後提腳都唔痛，只有向前提腳會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n上星期終於去左睇公立醫生，佢幫我檢查過，訓上床，對腳被佢左扭右扭之後話髖關節無事，無影X光。話拉傷⋯叫我休息下就送我走⋯<br />\n<br />\n晚晚有做伸展，好似無咩幫助咁，如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1Hvc8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1Hvc8v.png&h=49d8c1ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzPxrtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzPxrtv.jpg&h=a6e45c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傷左都成2星期，好抑鬱，做唔到運動⋯有無過來人分享下點醫「鼠蹊部」傷患？<br />\n睇左成個google相關資料，好似呢個位好難好，king James都經常傷呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗緊找脊醫/物理治療師睇睇，有無好介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68dc58a13910221beb6a7e22bdc24f81504736a9","tid":2409231,"uid":31361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"有無巴打都拉傷過呢個位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d4f7de939cf055e23295767f1988c67b86b604","tid":2409231,"uid":72932,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T18:26:32.000Z","msg":"你exactly邊個位痛 搵張肌肉圖圈一圈<br />\n整親拉根冇用的 唔使再拉嗰個位<br />\n <br />\nhip pain要screen都幾難打字講 有錢/保險就搵物理治療師 唔好搵脊醫<br />\n搵個有運動背景會好少少 如果剩係做電/針灸就唔使再去"},{"pid":"715efba09a1807116fc13060379104ae8ff07296","tid":2409231,"uid":88495,"like":1,"dislike":1