assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"跑多啲步   最初係會痛咗啲  <br />\n呢反應係俾你知肌肉啱啱先起步"},{"pid":"b8b479d66eb80ff6f97f1f48047d0f88fd5868c8","tid":2409231,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd3f489825aef8d4b0992d35d34e2181201ea6e2","tid":2409231,"uid":31361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"304034edf6539b6b324f98d6c471f32d4ddf086d","tid":2409231,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bfc1f0ac435f04bbeb44830b3cda8ee4728af33","tid":2409231,"uid":31361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上2星期行山行到左邊腳「鼠蹊部」，似拉傷，<br />\n頭幾日提腳都無力，3-4日後提到腳，但行路行10分鐘左右就開始痛⋯⋯⋯（左提腳，右提腳，後提腳都唔痛，只有向前提腳會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n上星期終於去左睇公立醫生，佢幫我檢查過，訓上床，對腳被佢左扭右扭之後話髖關節無事，無影X光。話拉傷⋯叫我休息下就送我走⋯<br />\n<br />\n晚晚有做伸展，好似無咩幫助咁，如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1Hvc8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1Hvc8v.png&h=49d8c1ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzPxrtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzPxrtv.jpg&h=a6e45c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傷左都成2星期，好抑鬱，做唔到運動⋯有無過來人分享下點醫「鼠蹊部」傷患？<br />\n睇左成個google相關資料，好似呢個位好難好，king James都經常傷呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗緊找脊醫/物理治療師睇睇，有無好介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"休息. <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"咁大劑⋯⋯巴打你個時就咁由得佢自己好？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6c4326553c7c17c18120c56f48bc9635a250e0","tid":2409231,"uid":347